      "string_number": 334,
      "type": "MESS",
      "source": "|cff8080ffNEW HERO|r\nDanath - captain of Anduin Lothar and nephew of the king Thoras Trollbane. Excellent warrior that can bash enemies with his shield and boost friendly units attack rate with his shouts."
    },
    "RoA_A01_M02_MESS_002": {
      "hash": "2cb581822e",
      "string_number": 333,
      "type": "MESS",
      "source": "|cff8080ffNEW SEMI HERO|r\nGavinrad - is one of the Azerothien veterans, who became the paladin of the Silver Hand order. Able to restore friendly units health with \"Healing Word\" and boost their melee attack with \"Vengeance Aura\"."
    },
